ently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methods</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>ArrayBuffer</code></strong> 物件是一種表示通用、固定大小的原始二進制資料緩衝。想要直接操作一個 <code>ArrayBuffer</code> 物件的內容是不可能的。若要讀寫該緩衝的內容則必須透過視圖，可以選擇建立一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a> 視圖物件或是一個限定其成員為某種型別的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>TypedArray</code></a> 視圖物件，它們皆能以特定的型別解讀、修改 <code>ArrayBuffer</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"語法","title":"語法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">new ArrayBuffer(length)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參數","title":"參數","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"length\"><code>length</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>要建立的緩衝陣列大小，以位元組（byte）計算。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"回傳值","title":"回傳值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>為一個新建立的指定大小 <code>ArrayBuffer</code> 物件，其內容皆初始化為 0。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RangeError\"><code>RangeError</code></a> is thrown if the <code>length</code> is larger than <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\"><code>Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (&gt;= 2 ** 53) or negative.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"說明","title":"說明","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor creates a new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> of the given length in bytes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"從既有的資料取得_arraybuffer","title":"從既有的資料取得 ArrayBuffer","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#appendix.3a_decode_a_base64_string_to_uint8array_or_arraybuffer\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">From a Base64 string (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader#readasarraybuffer()\">從本地端檔案</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.length\"><code>ArrayBuffer.length</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor's length property whose value is 1.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"get_arraybufferspecies_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The constructor function that is used to create derived objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.prototype\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Allows the addition of properties to all <code>ArrayBuffer</code> objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.isviewarg_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView(arg)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns <code>true</code> if <code>arg</code> is one of the ArrayBuffer views, such as <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\">typed array objects</a> or a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a>. Returns <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.transferoldbuffer_newbytelength\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>ArrayBuffer.transfer(oldBuffer [, newByteLength])</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a new <code>ArrayBuffer</code> whose contents are taken from the <code>oldBuffer</code>'s data and then is either truncated or zero-extended by <code>newByteLength</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arraybuffer_實例","title":"<code>ArrayBuffer</code> 實例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>所有的 <code>ArrayBuffer</code> 物件實例皆繼承自 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code></a>.</p>","titleAsText":"ArrayBuffer 實例"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性_2","title":"屬性","isH3":true,"content":"{{page('zh-TW/Web/JavaScript/JavaScript_typed_arrays/ArrayBuffer/prototype','屬性')}}"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法_2","title":"方法","isH3":true,"content":"{{page('/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/JavaScript_typed_arrays/ArrayBuffer/prototype','方法')}}\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer.slice_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Has the same functionality as <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In this example, we create a 8-byte buffer with a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> view referring to the buffer:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> view   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://tc39.es/ecma262/multipage/structured-data.html#sec-arraybuffer-objects","title":"ECMAScript Language Specification"}],"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.ArrayBuffer","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相容性備註","title":"相容性備註","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Starting with ECMAScript 2015, <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructors require to be constructed with a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\"><code>new</code></a> operator. Calling an <code>ArrayBuffer</code> constructor as a function without <code>new</code>, will throw a <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>TypeError</code></a> from now on.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError: calling a builtin ArrayBuffer constructor</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// without new is forbidden</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-good notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>TypedArray</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>SharedArrayBuffer</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"語法","id":"語法"},{"text":"說明","id":"說明"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"<code>ArrayBuffer</code> 實例","id":"arraybuffer_實例"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"相容性備註","id":"相容性備註"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"ArrayBuffer 物件是一種表示通用、固定大小的原始二進制資料緩衝。想要直接操作一個 ArrayBuffer 物件的內容是不可能的。若要讀寫該緩衝的內容則必須透過視圖，可以選擇建立一個 DataView 視圖物件或是一個限定其成員為某種型別的 TypedArray 視圖物件，它們皆能以特定的型別解讀、修改 ArrayBuffer。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"ArrayBuffer","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"tit